This is my first public Lora so it is still a little quirky. The model is particularly good at creating normal-looking people and weird dreamy atmospheres.

Between 1 and 2:

1.5 to add a slight layer of old-school

items.name: Murakumo (Senran Kagura)
items.description:
LoRA for Murakumo from Senran Kagura

The LoRA was trained on 167 images with 10 epochs, 32 dim and 16 alpha. The images were a mix of official/promotional art and fan art.

  • Use "black hair", "brown hair", "long hair", "parted bangs", "sidelocks", "ponytail", "side ponytail", "hair ornament", "hair ribbon", "oni mask", "mask on head" and "green eyes" for her looks.

  • Her "oni mask" and "hair ribbon" accessories can be removed if preferred. Simply don't include them or put them in the negative with weights if necessary.

  • Use "armor", "japanese armor", "shoulder armor", "japanese clothes", "cleavage", "haori", "kote", "kurokote", "kusazuri", "jacket", "red jacket", "open jacket", "floral print", "midriff", "underwear", "panties", "gauntlets" and "arm guards" to make her shinobi outfit. Add weights if necessary.

  • For her regular attire, use "sailor collar", "white sailor collar", "bowtie", "coat", "grey coat", "buttons", "sleeves", "long sleeves" and "buckle". Add weights if necessary.

Trained using this guide: https://civitai.com/models/22530

items.name: lewd limbo
items.description:
This is a pose in which the upper body is bent backward from the so-called "ero-shuwaku"
posture, with the bosom of the body protruding forward. It is not a limbo dance.

Prompt:.(limbo:1.3),spread legs,.
It seems that the stronger the key prompt is applied, the more limbo the dance will be.
LORA itself will also limbo more strongly, but since it will affect the pattern, it is better to
control net it after the ideal limbo and apply LORA thinly, so that the pattern will not be
affected as much.

Since we have learned various patterns of limbo, the composition of the limbo is rather variable. Please refer to the images for more information.

items.name: Iron Maiden Jeanne (Shaman King)
items.description:
If you like my works, consider make a donation.

The Iron Maiden, modern Joan of Arc, iron angel, holy maiden and one of the few catholic anime characters out there... Iron Maiden Jeanne!

Iron Maiden Jeanne is probably my favorite female character of all the Shonen Jump works. I remember when I watched the anime for the first time in 2004/5 and just by the voice I already knew that she would be a cute girl while she was hiding her appearance inside her Iron Maiden.

Unfortunately Hiroyuki Takei do this girl dirty, randomly marrying her to a character she barely interacts with, just because the protagonist's rival needed a wife just as important as the protagonist's wife; and after she's done her job of providing her husband with a child, the plot just kills her. That's why sometimes I think Shaman King should have stayed with the first anime ending and the manga stayed canceled. But we cannot change history, and we honor what was good.

This model was mainly made with scenes from the original anime rather than the 2021 one, to maintain consistency.

IMJeanne is the trigger word and she comes with three outfits.

  • Iron Maiden: iron tiara, iron dress, iron boots, iron bracelets

  • Casual: mobcap, white mobcap, jdress, black shoes

  • Pajamas: pink pajamas

silver hair, red eyes, long hair and bangs also helps.

I could be wrong, but if I'm not mistaken the pajamas are an exclusive outfit from the original anime to censor the scenes she was naked in the manga.

Her Iron Maiden outfit is complex, even though the model has been trained mostly in this outfit there may be strange results compared to other clothes. Be warned.

I recommend using this model with weight 0.7.

but is she in distress ? -soul3142

RECOMMENDATIONS :-

Use LoRA name according to the downloaded file when copying example prompts.

  1. Highres Fix - If you are getting blurry and ugly images & try reducing LoRA weight

    My upscale method: txt2img 512x768 -> send to img2img -> controlnet tile upscale, tile diffusion 2x scale with 4xUltrasharp upscaler and tiled vae

  1. Weight: 0.55 - 0.75

  2. Clip Skip: 2

  3. Denoising - Don't go too high, it can alter a lot of details

  4. For better face's - you can use ADetailer

Some LoRA's are flexible with any clothing, some are not so keep these things in mind.

items.name: Billions of Creatures - Standalone
items.description:
With YAML-files you just get 1 nice wildcard-file Instead of 100 files. They are easy readable (best with Notepadd++) and they are easy to maintain.

Don't forget to leave a ‚ù§Ô∏è to get a notification for future updates. ‚≠ê reviews are appreciated, too. Let me see what you created with this tool. ;)

note: Yaml files will throw isseus when using: "a1111-sd-webui-tagcomplete"extension. That's related to the extension, not the wildcards.

Usage

Unleash the full power:

Activate: Dynamic Prompts->Advanced Options->Unlink seed from prompt

Usage is pretty much the same as for "regular" wildcards.

You need the SD Dynamic Prompt Extension. Put the files directly into the wildcard folder:

~\stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-dynamic-prompts\wildcards

They show up as a menu on the left in the Wildcards tab.

The YAML is structured and indented (that's how they work). Just with a little difference. You have to add the category layers in the wildcard.

Examples:

__BoCreatures/random__

I made easy to use wildcards for character creations.

You are welcome

Leave a star review, if you like it. so other can find those awesome cards more easily.

I plan to add more themes as extensions in the future. SDXL is coming, and wildcards are limitless.

If you want to support me, feel free to buy me a coffee. ;)

Have experimenting with it.

items.description:
Brief

This is a multi-identifier Lora of Bronya Zaychik Silverwing from Honkai impact. I have included all 4 costumes in game into one Lora, and you can easily switch between them with prompts

Lora weight suggest to set between 0.7-0.9, if you want to change to other costume other than the 4 included, 0.9 should work as well, otherwise lower to 0.7.

Changing costume

The 4 costumes can be changed easily with the prompts belowÔºå where red is the trigger, and blue is the additional prompts for better accuracy (remove some if you don`t want Bronya to wear all of them)

The default Silverwing costume: bronya zaychik \(silverwing: n-ex\), sleeveless dress, single glove, single thighhigh, earrings, single sleeve, halterneck, single pauldron, boots

The China dress costume: bronya-qipao, mismatched gloves, china dress, asymmetrical legwear, sunglasses, black footwear, white shorts, single pauldron

The non-official office lady suit: bronya-OL, pencil skirt, high heels, black jacket, id card, striped shirt, earrings

The official office lady suit: bronya-OL2, suit jacket, thighband pantyhose, gloves, id card, high heels, high-waist skirt, ribbed sweater

P.S. This is the first model I did on a 6-GPU rig, thanks for Kingzet for providing the server!
